  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00103', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-112-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設一含有外貿部門的凱因斯模型如下：C 100 0.8Y，Y =Y T，T 50，I 100，G 50，X 150， d d M 60 0.05Y，其中Y為所得，C為消費，I為投資，G為政府支出，X為出口，M為進口，T為 = + − = = = = 定額稅收，則均衡所得是多少？ = +', '["900", "1,000", "1,200", "1,500"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0827882f64ba", "answer_pdf_sha1": "46a7f3212c67", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112200", "c": "318", "s": "1501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00104', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-112-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設為了避免新臺幣持續貶值，中央銀行動用外匯存底進場干預外匯市場，根據凱因斯IS-LM模 型，在其他條件不變下，最可能導致下述何種情形發生？', '["利率上揚、產出減少", "利率上揚、產出增加", "利率下跌、產出減少", "利率下跌、產出增加"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0827882f64ba", "answer_pdf_sha1": "46a7f3212c67", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112200", "c": "318", "s": "1501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00105', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-112-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一個100人的小鎮，其中有20個小孩年紀未滿15歲，8人是退休人員，50人有全職工作， 4人有兼職工作，8人是年滿15歲的全職學生，4人是全職家庭主婦，剩下的目前都沒有工作但 在找工作中，則這個小鎮的失業率與勞動參與率分別是多少？', '["10.0%、75.0%", "10.0%、80.0%", "16.7%、75.0%", "16.7%、80.0%"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0827882f64ba", "answer_pdf_sha1": "46a7f3212c67", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112200", "c": "318", "s": "1501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
